{"name":"Indomitable","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Requirement </strong>You are not mounted</p>\n<p><strong>Grants</strong> @Compendium[pf2e-vanguard.vanguard-effects.hoMY1timrdXv2ANF]{Stance: Indomitable}</p>\n<hr />\n<p>While in this stance, you are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 1}, your speed becomes 15 regardless of bonuses and penalties to speed, and you can ignore the first square of difficult terrain while Striding. However, your melee strikes deal an additional 2 damage. This extra damage increases to 7 when you have steel path, or to 13 when you have adamantine path.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Volume of the Vanguard"},"traits":{"value":["stance","hb_vanguard"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.738,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-04-19T21:45:33.666-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.8.4.11118"}}},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.kradiX55cggeBzyr"}},"_id":"Bwo5JFVhaYygTCqP"}
{"_id":"CYLr6bwg6mU6sHXU","name":"Active Defense (Intuitive)","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You hold a protective form, granting your armor the redoubt trait, but keyed to Wisdom instead of Intelligence. This allows you to use Wisdom instead of Dexterity for AC (limited by Max Dex, &amp; not currently automated), and instead of Dexterity for Reflex Saves (automated). However, when active, you take a -2 penalty to both Will &amp; Reflex Saves, due to over-taxing your instincts, unless you continue using Dexterity for Reflex saves (due to Foundry limitations on the AC implmentation, it's easiest to leave the toggle off if you do so, applying a custom modifier to your AC)</p>"},"source":{"value":"Volume of the Vanguard"},"traits":{"value":["stance"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"ability":"wis","key":"FlatModifier","label":"Wisdom (intuitive redoubt)","selector":"reflex","type":"ability","predicate":{"all":["activated-pangolin-kit"]}},{"key":"RollOption","domain":"all","option":"activated-pangolin-kit","label":"In Active Defense","toggleable":true},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Taxed Instincts","selector":"will","type":"untyped","value":-2,"predicate":{"all":["activated-pangolin-kit"]}},{"key":"FlatModifier","label":"Taxed Instincts","selector":"reflex","type":"untyped","value":-2,"predicate":{"all":["activated-pangolin-kit"]}}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.738,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-04-22T00:04:25.677-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.8.4.11118"}}},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"defensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.LiNPoJ9Eh427UDxF"}}}
