{"name":"Dragon's Breath","type":"action","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You use the breath weapon for your chosen dragon type, with the shape described in the @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.JcobNl4iE9HmMYtE]{Dragon Breath} sorcerer bloodline spell. This breath deals 1d6 damage per character level (&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">[[/r max(0, @actor.level)d6[dragon]]]{leveled damage} )</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">. Once you use this ability, you can't use it again for 3 rounds.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>When you have Adamantine Path, this damage increases to&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">[[/r max(0, @actor.level)d10[dragon]]]{1d10 per level}</span></p>\n<p>Draggable areas:</p>\n<p>@Template[type:cone|distance:30], @Template[type:line|distance:60], @Template[type:burst|distance:10]</p>\n<p>Saves:</p>\n<p>@Check[type:fortitude|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classDC.value)|basic:true] <span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Check[type:reflex|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classDC.value)|basic:true] </span><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">@Check[type:will|dc:resolve(@actor.attributes.classDC.value)|basic:true]</span></p>\n<table class=\"pf2-table\" style=\"width: 737px;\">\n<thead style=\"text-shadow: 1px 1px var(--color-shadow-dark); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\">\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 218px;\">Dragon Type</th>\n<th style=\"width: 370px;\">Area and damage type</th>\n<th style=\"width: 148px;\">Saving Throw</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Black, Brine, or Copper</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">60-foot line of acid</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Blue or Bronze</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">60-foot line of electricity</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Brass</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">60-foot line of fire</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Cloud</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of electricity</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Crystal or Forest</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of piercing</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Green</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of poison</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Fortitude</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Gold, Magma, or Red</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of fire</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Sea</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">10-foot burst within 30 feet of bludgeoning</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Silver or White</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of cold</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Sky</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">10-foot burst within 30 feet of electricity</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Sovereign</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of mental</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Will</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Umbral</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">30-foot cone of negative</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 218px;\">Underworld</td>\n<td style=\"width: 370px;\">10-foot burst within 30 feet of fire</td>\n<td style=\"width: 148px;\">Reflex</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>"},"source":{"value":"Volume of the Vanguard"},"traits":{"value":["hb_vanguard"],"rari